{"tid":1224264,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"接受暫緩對唔對撚得住一眾犧牲者啊dllm","createTime":"2019-06-15T02:44:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T14:53:29.000Z","uid":35927,"like":206,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"73ed82f297929e616b4cd0b7b944e628bf3b22e7","tid":1224264,"uid":35927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:44:47.000Z","msg":"對得住中咗彈嘅肺癌伯伯咩！<br />\n對得住口吐鮮血嘅義士咩！<br />\n對得住女拔嗰位眼中彈嘅男老師咩！<br />\n對得住被人非禮被人用盾鋤落去嘅女仔咩！<br />\n心郁郁想妥協嘅人，你地對得住已經犧牲受傷被捕嘅人咩！<br />\n再問問自己，對唔對得住香港，對唔對得住自己嘅初心！<br />\n<br />\n咪撚再講咩暫緩、階段性勝利啊，我地要嘅係撤回引渡條例、追究林鄭班狗官同黑警嘅責任、仲有釋放被捕義士，唔係乜撚嘢暫緩啊dllm"},{"pid":"4829699022a5f3c8c840001fad7f9dda2df669a7","tid":1224264,"uid":258956,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:45:39.000Z","msg":"暫你老母！"},{"pid":"04751da0258ed917f7e82db679136c95cf4f2ca2","tid":1224264,"uid":52221,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:46:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Yc1B4LBSfkE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FYc1B4LBSfkE&d=MAn3riz0%2FQ%2FS8BFDrurXlQHlXPv3B7QU%2BsV1%2BUkEKpk%3D&h=3fbc7471\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Yc1B4LBSfkE</a>"},{"pid":"0bfb1ab488f36e8cd34d8dabd6c37e47b4825c3a","tid":1224264,"uid":33045,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:47:19.000Z","msg":"如果有人強姦緊你，突然有外賣送到，佢暫緩強姦你，你O唔OK ？"},{"pid":"2268cd124c08a6b7f27a43fcb5f4f66aad5f7d01","tid":1224264,"uid":215876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:47:42.000Z","msg":"推呀,6月16出"},{"pid":"7e7571710770485d233e1a8be5d2f88fd6892b16","tid":1224264,"uid":22362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:49:30.000Z","msg":"冇錯"},{"pid":"98d9e5e97ad0a34186eded76e29bfb4c8914f858","tid":1224264,"uid":137493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:49:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fed215beff9bdafbdef702860eb08d5b5593b33e","tid":1224264,"uid":36592,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:49:47.000Z","msg":"[緊急/請廣傳] 政府暫緩以退為進，星期日香港人唔出嚟將會一敗塗地<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1224213\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1224213</a><br />\n<br />\n經過69百萬人遊行同612血腥鎮壓，政府既管治合法性已經危在旦夕，全世界都等緊機會作致命一擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家政府扮聽民意暫緩修例，目的係以退為進，買時間令善忘既香港人沖淡怒氣，同時令國際社會無機會出手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果香港人因為政府暫緩而星期日唔出嚟，之後將會係連場既大規模清算同白色恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到時候無人會再敢抗爭，惡法原封不動通過，69既百萬人遊行，612義士既犧牲將會毀於一旦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果你唔想呢件事發生，就要趁全世界站係香港人一方，民氣最強既時候出黎遊行，堅持撤回<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢場仗冇階段性勝利，一係贏，一係輸，winner takes all<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港要贏，香港人星期日一定要出嚟，多你一個絕對好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n緊記目標只有一個：撤回惡法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n請大家copy呢個post喺Facebook, IG, Whatsapp share出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n文宣組幫手整圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用盡你一切方法動員認識既人星期日出嚟堅持撤回<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f702b65a79980d549ef4cfddaa2826fd5db1682b","tid":1224264,"uid":105924,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:50:34.000Z","msg":"點都會出，香港人咁都收貨既話下次真係連屎都會接受到"},{"pid":"ede10229cb9e0886368e4405a84950c57c5f1ba3","tid":1224264,"uid":19278,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:51:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">不撤不散</span>"},{"pid":"8559e0f654e74a83d6da05a17cdeec12a0438278","tid":1224264,"uid":111578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":